voices.mp3Text: Tis no treason to kill a tyrant king.

voices.mp3Text: When you strike a king's neck, you better take his head.

voices.mp3Text: The day has eyes. Night, ears. The wolf, teeth.

voices.mp3Text: Even you should fear the full moon.
voices.name: Night Stalker

voices.mp3Text: The night needs nobility, not a beastly fairy tale.
voices.name: Night Stalker

voices.mp3Text: Stop complaining. You're already a skeleton for God's sake.

voices.mp3Text: A boar is a wolf's natural prey.

voices.mp3Text: Your sacrifice shall not be forgotten.
